Name: Sir Stretchalot - The Wenches in the Well
About the game: Put on the helmet and become more than a man! Become Sir Stretchalot, a Stretcher who travels the land, saving the day and stretching hotties, whether they be Monster Girls , regular girls, or anything in between. If it can be stretched, Sir Stretchalot will stretch it. Sir Stretchalot - 'The Wenches in the Well' includes cut-scenes and a simple JRPG combat system that players will find easy to understand and use. There is some dungeon crawling, the game is very narrative heavy, and contains over 18k words of dialogue.
